1.13
log
@Provide a timecounter based on the UltraSPARC IIe STICK logic.
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: psychoreg.h,v 1.12 2008/07/12 13:08:04 kettenis Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: psychoreg.h,v 1.6.4.2 2001/09/13 01:14:40 thorpej Exp $ */

